# Project Context — SweetFlow (bassata-oms)

**Product:** Velora — نظام كاشير وإدارة فروع (multi-location POS + light ERP).  
**Repo:** `bassata-oms` · package still `cafeflow-erp-pos` · UI kit folder: `SweetFlow`.

## Stack

- Next.js 16 App Router · React 19 · Tailwind 4
- Supabase (Auth, Postgres, RLS, Storage)
- shadcn (base-nova) + **SweetFlow** composites (`src/components/SweetFlow/*`)
- TanStack Table · Zustand · RHF+Zod · sonner
- Edge session: `src/proxy.ts` (not legacy middleware assumptions)

## Architecture

```
src/app/(shell|operational|auth|print)/  → thin routes
src/modules/<domain>/{actions,services,components}
src/lib/repositories/ · src/lib/auth/ · src/stores/
```

## UI language

Arabic-first RTL (`lang="ar"` `dir="rtl"`, Cairo). Shared chrome via `t()`; many ops labels hardcoded Arabic. Public QR menu at `/menu`.

## Design reference

Follow `docs/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md` and existing SweetFlow primitives (`PageHeader`, `OperationalCard`, `DataTableShell`, `StandardModal`, state blocks). Do not add a second design system.

